<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#2bc59f6d85fc7ce3c5964fbb915464d4>.
<#2bc59f6d85fc7ce3c5964fbb915464d4> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
