<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#78dddc3f4ea1762794369a51601665bc>.
<#78dddc3f4ea1762794369a51601665bc> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dataset/ucl/doi-10-14428/DVN/OLMRXF>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:32:55.565Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#78dddc3f4ea1762794369a51601665bc> {
<http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dataset/ucl/doi-10-14428/DVN/OLMRXF> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "doi:10.14428/DVN/OLMRXF";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Experimental Investigation of a Methanol Fueled SI Engine at Full Load Using a Central Composite Design"@en, "Experimenteel onderzoek van een Methanol-aangedreven SI-motor bij volledige belasting met behulp van een centraal composietontwerp"@nl-t-en, "Étude expérimentale d'un moteur SI alimenté au méthanol à pleine charge à l'aide d'une conception composite centrale"@fr-t-en, "Experimentelle Untersuchung eines mit Methanol betriebenen SI-Motors bei Volllast unter Verwendung einer zentralen Verbundkonstruktion"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The large difference in fuel properties between methanol and gasoline demand the development of a dedicated spark ignition (SI) engine in order to exploit methanol’s properties for maximum thermal efficiency, rather than using the flex-fuel engines of today"@en, "Het grote verschil in brandstofeigenschappen tussen methanol en benzine vereist de ontwikkeling van een speciale motor met vonkontsteking (SI) om de eigenschappen van methanol te benutten voor maximale thermische efficiëntie, in plaats van de huidige flexfuelmotoren te gebruiken."@nl-t-en, "La grande différence de propriétés du carburant entre le méthanol et l’essence nécessite le développement d’un moteur à allumage par étincelles (SI) dédié afin d’exploiter les propriétés du méthanol pour une efficacité thermique maximale, plutôt que d’utiliser les moteurs à carburant flexible d’aujourd’hui."@fr-t-en, "Der große Unterschied in den Kraftstoffeigenschaften zwischen Methanol und Benzin erfordert die Entwicklung eines speziellen Fremdzündungsmotors (SI), um die Eigenschaften von Methanol für einen maximalen thermischen Wirkungsgrad zu nutzen, anstatt die Flex-Fuel-Motoren von heute zu verwenden."@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2022-08-26T11:42:50Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2022-08-26T11:43:27Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2022-08-26T11:43:27Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#version> "1";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeRegisteredEntity/0419052272>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4468-5518>, <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2421-580X>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Spark ignition engine"@en, "variable valve timing"@en, "dual fuel engines"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> "Engineering";
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TECH>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.14428/DVN/OLMRXF>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/bibliographicCitation> "Suijs Ward; Verhelst Sebastian, 2022, \"Experimental Investigation of a Methanol Fueled SI Engine at Full Load Using a Central Composite Design\", https://doi.org/10.14428/DVN/OLMRXF, Open Data @ UCLouvain, V1";
    <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/citedBy> _:b54125_b54124_b54123_df_12_69110;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b54125_b54124_b54123_df_12_69111.
_:b54125_b54124_b54123_df_12_69110 a <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Document>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Suijs, W. and Verhelst, S., \"Experimental Investigation of a Methanol Fueled SI Engine at Full Load Using a Central Composite Design,\" SAE Technical Paper 2022-01-0517, 2022";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "10.4271/2022-01-0517";
    <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/uri> <https://doi.org/10.4271/2022-01-0517.>.
_:b54125_b54124_b54123_df_12_69111 a <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Kind>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#fn> "Dias, Véronique";
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasOrganizationName> "Universite catholique de Louvain";
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasEmail> <mailto:veronique.dias@uclouvain.be>
