    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Fabric reference, contact angles, roll-off angles, profilometry images"@en, "Stofreferentie, contacthoeken, afrolhoeken, profilometriebeelden"@nl-t-en, "Référence du tissu, angles de contact, angles d'enroulement, images de profilométrie"@fr-t-en, "Stoffbezug, Kontaktwinkel, Abrollwinkel, Profilometriebilder"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Useful id information + contact angles and roll-off angles + profilometry images as reported in \n\nJonas, A.M.; Cai, R.; Vermeyen, R.; Nysten, B.; Vanneste, M.; De Smet, D.; Glinel, K., How roughness controls the water repellency of woven fabrics, Materials & Design 2020, 187, 108389 (https://doi.org/10.1016/j.matdes.2019.108389)."@en, "Nuttige id-informatie + contacthoeken en afrolhoeken + profilometriebeelden zoals gerapporteerd in\n\nJonas, A.M.; Cai, R.; Vermeyen, R.; Nysten, B.; Vanneste, M.; De Smet, D.; Glinel, K., How roughness controls the water repellency of woven fabrics, Materials & Design 2020, 187, 108389 (https://doi.org/10.1016/j.matdes.2019.108389)."@nl-t-en, "Informations utiles sur l'identifiant + angles de contact et angles d'enroulement + images de profilométrie comme indiqué dans\n\nJonas, A.M.; Cai, R.; Vermeyen, R.; Nysten, B.; Vanneste, M.; De Smet, D.; Glinel, K., How rugness controls the water repellency of woven fabrics, Materials & Design 2020, 187, 108389 (https://doi.org/10.1016/j.matdes.2019.108389)."@fr-t-en, "Nützliche ID-Informationen + Kontaktwinkel und Abrollwinkel + Profilometriebilder wie in\n\nJonas, A.M.; Cai, R.; Vermeyen, R.; Nysten, B.; Vanneste, M.; De Smet, D.; Glinel, K., How roughness controls the water repellency of woven fabrics, Materials & Design 2020, 187, 108389 (https://doi.org/10.1016/j.matdes.2019.108389)."@de-t-en;
