<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#5c86085a6d53ffe64524854a4e79ac02>.
<#5c86085a6d53ffe64524854a4e79ac02> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dataset/ucl/doi-10-14428/DVN/25VGBX>;
