<#06ae30a961fa95c2807d5de6b9481612> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dataset/ucl/doi-10-14428/DVN/9YTIBF>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:32:55.809Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#06ae30a961fa95c2807d5de6b9481612> {
<http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dataset/ucl/doi-10-14428/DVN/9YTIBF> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "doi:10.14428/DVN/9YTIBF";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Videos of rebounds on Matumi fabric (Fabric 4 of article)"@en, "Video's van rebounds op Matumi stof (Fabric 4 van artikel)"@nl-t-en, "Vidéos de rebonds sur tissu Matumi (Tissu 4 de l'article)"@fr-t-en, "Videos von Rebounds auf Matumi Stoff (Stoff 4 des Artikels)"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Videos (mp4 format) of droplets impacting fabrics. \n\n\nFilename Format: Fabric_Coating_DroppingHeight(cm)_DropletVolume(uL) \n\nCoating names: PhobRSH: wax-based coating; PDMS: silicone rubber; CF4 or C4F: perfluorobutyl-based\n\nFrame rate:  ca. 900 frames per second\n\nPixel size:  ca. 16.7 micrometers\n\n\nMight also be applicable: \nFabric_Coating_DroppingHeight(cm)_DropletVolume(uL)_TrialNumber\n\nFabric_Coating_DroppingHeight(cm)_DropletVolume(uL)_FrameRate_TrialNumber"@en, "Video's (mp4-formaat) van druppels die stoffen beïnvloeden. \n\n\nBestandsnaam Formaat: Fabric_Coating_DroppingHoogte (cm)_DropletVolume (uL)\n\nNaam van de coating: PhobRSH: coating op basis van was; PDMS: siliconenrubber; CF4 of C4F: op basis van perfluorbutyl\n\nHet tarief van het kader: ca. 900 beelden per seconde\n\nPixelgrootte: ca. 16,7 micrometer\n\n\nKan ook van toepassing zijn: \nFabric_Coating_DroppingHoogte(cm)_DropletVolume(uL)_TrialNumber \n\nFabric_Coating_DroppingHoogte(cm)_DropletVolume(uL)_FrameRate_TrialNumber"@nl-t-en, "Vidéos (format mp4) de gouttelettes impactant les tissus. \n\n\nFormat du nom de fichier: Tissu_Coating_DroppingHeight(cm)_DropletVolume(uL)\n\nNoms des revêtements: PhobRSH : revêtement à base de cire; PDMS : caoutchouc de silicone; CF4 ou C4F: à base de perfluorobutyle\n\nFréquence d'images: environ 900 images par seconde\n\nTaille du pixel: environ 16,7 micromètres\n\n\nPeut également s'appliquer: \nTissu_Coating_DroppingHeight(cm)_DropletVolume(uL)_TrialNumber \n\nTissu_Coating_DroppingHeight(cm)_DropletVolume(uL)_FrameRate_TrialNumber"@fr-t-en, "Videos (mp4-Format) von Tröpfchen, die Stoffe beeinflussen. \n\n\nFormat der Datei: Stoff_Beschichtung_DroppingHeight(cm)_DropletVolume(uL)\n\nBezeichnungen der Beschichtung: PhobRSH: Beschichtung auf Wachsbasis; PDMS: Silikonkautschuk; CF4 oder C4F: auf Perfluorbutylbasis\n\nBildrate: ca. 900 Bilder pro Sekunde\n\nPixelgröße: ca. 16,7 Mikrometer\n\n\nKönnte auch anwendbar sein: \nStoff_Beschichtung_DroppingHeight(cm)_DropletVolume(uL)_TrialNumber \n\nFabric_Coating_DroppingHeight(cm)_DropletVolume(uL)_FrameRate_TrialNummer"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2021-09-28T10:41:21Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2021-10-05T07:26:14Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2021-10-05T07:26:14Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#version> "1";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeRegisteredEntity/0419052272>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4083-0688>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> "Chemistry";
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TECH>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.14428/DVN/9YTIBF>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/bibliographicCitation> "Jonas, Alain, 2021, \"Videos of rebounds on Matumi fabric (Fabric 4 of article)\", https://doi.org/10.14428/DVN/9YTIBF, Open Data @ UCLouvain, V1";
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b54266_b54265_b54264_df_12_69179.
_:b54266_b54265_b54264_df_12_69179 a <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Kind>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#fn> "Jonas, Alain";
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasOrganizationName> "Universite catholique de Louvain";
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasEmail> <mailto:alain.jonas@uclouvain.be>
}
<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#3694c2b58e348ed31af4536ebeaf4ce1>.
<#3694c2b58e348ed31af4536ebeaf4ce1> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dataset/ucl/doi-10-14428/DVN/JKHEZE>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:32:55.814Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#3694c2b58e348ed31af4536ebeaf4ce1> {
<http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dataset/ucl/doi-10-14428/DVN/JKHEZE> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "doi:10.14428/DVN/JKHEZE";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Large Eddy Simulation of rich ammonia/hydrogen/ air combustion in a gas turbine burner"@en, "Grote Eddy Simulatie van rijke ammoniak/waterstof/luchtverbranding in een gasturbinebrander"@nl-t-en, "Large Eddy Simulation de la combustion riche en ammoniac/hydrogène/air dans un brûleur à turbine à gaz"@fr-t-en, "Große Wirbelsimulation der reichen Ammoniak-/Wasserstoff-/Luftverbrennung in einem Gasturbinenbrenner"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Paper on \n- Combustion characteristics of NH3/H2 blends were explored from 1D simulations.\n- NOX/NH3 emissions trade-off is found for a precise equivalence ratio in rich blends.\n- The equivalence ratio at emissions trade-off increases with hydrogen addition.\n- 3D LES yields NOX/NH3 emissions of ~300 ppmv for f ¼ 1:46 and XFuel\nH2¼ 0:46."@en, "Document over\nVerbrandingskenmerken van NH3/H2-mengsels werden onderzocht aan de hand van 1D-simulaties.\n- NOX/NH3-emissieafweging wordt gevonden voor een precieze equivalentieverhouding in rijke mengsels.\n- De equivalentieverhouding bij emissieafweging neemt toe met de toevoeging van waterstof.\n- 3D LES levert NOX/NH3 emissies van ~300 ppmv voor f 1⁄4 1:46 en XFuel \nH21⁄4 0:46."@nl-t-en, "Document sur\n- Les caractéristiques de combustion des mélanges NH3/H2 ont été explorées à partir de simulations 1D.\n- Un compromis entre les émissions de NOX et de NH3 est trouvé pour un rapport d'équivalence précis dans les mélanges riches.\n- Le ratio d’équivalence au compromis sur les émissions augmente avec l’ajout d’hydrogène.\n- 3D LES produit des émissions de NOX/NH3 d'environ 300 ppmv pour f 1⁄4 1:46 et XFuel \nH21⁄4 0:46."@fr-t-en, "Papier über\n- Die Verbrennungseigenschaften von NH3/H2-Mischungen wurden anhand von 1D-Simulationen untersucht.\n- NOX/NH3-Emissionskompromittierung wird für ein genaues Äquivalenzverhältnis in reichhaltigen Mischungen gefunden.\n- Das Äquivalenzverhältnis beim Emissionsausgleich steigt mit der Wasserstoffzugabe.\n- 3D LES liefert NOX/NH3-Emissionen von ~300 ppmv für f 1⁄4 1:46 und XFuel \nH21⁄4 0:46."@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2022-08-26T10:51:51Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2022-08-26T10:52:28Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2022-08-26T10:52:28Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
