<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#bb6a26d3ab424ce2e1f3a0dfa7d3ce87>.
<#bb6a26d3ab424ce2e1f3a0dfa7d3ce87> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
