<#934f3b16249db3106f2e505677ae97a9> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dataset/ucl/doi-10-14428/DVN/N47CFQ>;
