    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/bibliographicCitation> "Araz, Jack Y., 2020, \"Implementation of a search for supersymmetry in the multijet (2 to 6 jets) + missing energy channel (36.1/fb; 13 TeV; ATLAS-SUSY-2016-07)\", https://doi.org/10.14428/DVN/N47CFQ, Open Data @ UCLouvain, V3";
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b54320_b54319_b54318_df_12_69204;
