    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Bricteux, L., Duponcheel, M., Winckelmans, G., Tiselj, I., & Bartosiewicz, Y. Direct and large eddy simulation of turbulent heat transfer at very low Prandtl number: Application to lead–bismuth flows. Nuclear engineering and design, 246, 91-97, (2012)";
