<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#341011ad0dde92a1ca4ab8ce0772dc72>.
<#341011ad0dde92a1ca4ab8ce0772dc72> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
