    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "doi:10.14428/DVN/3KIN1Q";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "The Role of Electrofuels under Uncertainties for the Belgian Energy Transition"@en, "De rol van elektrobrandstoffen onder onzekerheden voor de Belgische energietransitie"@nl-t-en, "Le rôle des électrocarburants dans les incertitudes pour la transition énergétique belge"@fr-t-en, "Die Rolle von Elektrokraftstoffen bei Unsicherheiten für die belgische Energiewende"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The paper highlights the role of electrofuels (i.e., hydrogen, electro-methane, and\nelectro-liquid fuels) under uncertainties in the Belgian whole-energy (i.e., multi-sector\nand multi-carrier) system in 2050 at different level of greenhouse gas (GHG) emissions\nmitigation, i.e., “climate targets”."@en, "Het document benadrukt de rol van elektrobrandstoffen (d.w.z. waterstof, elektromethaan en\nelektro-vloeibare brandstoffen) onder onzekerheden in de Belgische volledige energie (d.w.z. multisectoraal\nen multi-carrier) systeem in 2050 op verschillende niveaus van broeikasgasemissies (BKG) \nmitigatie, d.w.z. “klimaatdoelstellingen”."@nl-t-en, "L'article met en évidence le rôle des électrocarburants (c'est-à-dire l'hydrogène, l'électrométhane et\ncombustibles électroliquides) sous l'incertitude de l'ensemble de l'énergie belge (c'est-à-dire multisectorielle\net multi-transporteurs) en 2050 à différents niveaux d'émissions de gaz à effet de serre (GES) \nl’atténuation, c’est-à-dire les «objectifs climatiques»."@fr-t-en, "Der Beitrag beleuchtet die Rolle von Elektrokraftstoffen (z.B. Wasserstoff, Elektromethan und\nElektro-Flüssig-Brennstoffe) unter Unsicherheiten im belgischen Gesamtenergiesektor (d. h. in mehreren Sektoren)\nund Multi-Carrier-System im Jahr 2050 auf unterschiedlichem Niveau der Treibhausgasemissionen (THG-Emissionen) \nAbschwächung, d. h. „Klimaziele“."@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2022-08-26T11:37:04Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2022-08-26T11:37:29Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2022-08-26T11:37:29Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#version> "1";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeRegisteredEntity/0419052272>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/e0b1a4536176d636a39950bc15e2eeb42e35ab0a>, <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0368-8544>, <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2371-8210>, <https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5473-8762>, <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-8341-4350>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "electrofuels"@en, "energy transition"@en, "energy system modelling"@en, "sensitivity analysis"@en, "EnergyScope TD"@en, "polynomial chaos expansion"@en, "sectors coupling"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> "Engineering";
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TECH>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.14428/DVN/3KIN1Q>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/bibliographicCitation> "Rixhon Xavier; Limpens Gauthier; Coppitters Diederik; Jeanmart Hervé; Contino Francesco, 2022, \"The Role of Electrofuels under Uncertainties for the Belgian Energy Transition\", https://doi.org/10.14428/DVN/3KIN1Q, Open Data @ UCLouvain, V1";
    <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/citedBy> _:b54392_b54391_b54390_df_12_69251;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b54392_b54391_b54390_df_12_69252;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dist/ucl/s3-//dataverse-182da5ead38-b87aae4141f1>.
_:b54392_b54391_b54390_df_12_69251 a <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Document>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "The Role of Electrofuels under Uncertainties for the Belgian Energy Transition by Xavier Rixhon, Gauthier Limpens, Diederik Coppitters, Hervé Jeanmart and Francesco Contino – Energies 2021, 14, 4027";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "10.3390/en14134027";
    <http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/uri> <https://doi.org/10.3390/en14134027>.
_:b54392_b54391_b54390_df_12_69252 a <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Kind>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#fn> "Dias, Véronique";
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasOrganizationName> "Universite catholique de Louvain";
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasEmail> <mailto:veronique.dias@uclouvain.be>
}
<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#780fc49ae3a634533c50b7268255e050>.
<#780fc49ae3a634533c50b7268255e050> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dataset/ucl/doi-10-14428/DVN/HF01QB>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:32:56.030Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#780fc49ae3a634533c50b7268255e050> {
<http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/dataset/ucl/doi-10-14428/DVN/HF01QB> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "doi:10.14428/DVN/HF01QB";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Replication Data for: \"Jacaric acid empowers RSL3-induced ferroptotic cell death in both 2D and 3D breast cancer models\""@en, "Replicatiegegevens voor: \"Jacarinezuur bekrachtigt RSL3-geïnduceerde ferroptotische celdood in zowel 2D- als 3D-borstkankermodellen\""@nl-t-en, "Données de réplication pour: L'acide jacarique renforce la mort cellulaire ferroptotique induite par RSL3 dans les modèles de cancer du sein 2D et 3D"@fr-t-en, "Replikationsdaten für: Jacarinsäure ermöglicht RSL3-induzierten ferroptotischen Zelltod sowohl in 2D- als auch in 3D-Brustkrebsmodellen"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Lipidomic analysis was performed on two breast cancer cell lines, Hs578T and MCF7, belonging to the triple negative and luminal A subtypes, respectively, to determine which lipid species jacaric acid (JA) was incorporated into and to what extent, in order to precise the mechanism behind JA-induced ferroptosis in these cell lines."@en, "Lipidomische analyse werd uitgevoerd op twee borstkankercellijnen, Hs578T en MCF7, die behoren tot de drievoudige negatieve en luminale A-subtypen, respectievelijk, om te bepalen in welke lipidesoort jacarinezuur (JA) werd opgenomen en in welke mate, om het mechanisme achter JA-geïnduceerde ferroptose in deze cellijnen te preciseren."@nl-t-en, "Une analyse lipodomique a été effectuée sur deux lignées cellulaires de cancer du sein, Hs578T et MCF7, appartenant respectivement aux sous-types A triple négatif et A luminal, afin de déterminer dans quelle espèce lipidique l'acide jacarique (JA) a été incorporé et dans quelle mesure, afin de préciser le mécanisme derrière la ferroptose induite par JA dans ces lignées cellulaires."@fr-t-en, "Lipidomische Analysen wurden an zwei Brustkrebs-Zelllinien, Hs578T und MCF7, die zu den dreifach negativen bzw. luminalen A-Subtypen gehören, durchgeführt, um zu bestimmen, in welche Lipidspezies Jacarinsäure (JA) integriert wurde und in welchem Umfang, um den Mechanismus der JA-induzierten Ferroptose in diesen Zelllinien zu präzisieren."@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2024-11-19T10:19:05Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2024-12-12T09:29:56Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-12-12T09:29:56Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#version> "1";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeRegisteredEntity/0419052272>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/25e97f3f1f00b408989cd313d7c8fccec5c661b1>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/d3bb9ee09e5d972e79a1dcdee6a9827989ad8fe8>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/0a4b2f26bf9b44244005e8422aac45fc218593d3>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/2b1c1c43eb794b22418958774fd34cd7dfb162d9>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/8f8b00a160280234f53c91ee628a34a2d8c26e39>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/abf07ebb5fc76c9fdb5e1abf38c7ac10bed78a89>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/728c6431d90e04669e2281fe0738e9ed485f02c9>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/49ebad532854f8f760145b2ceca9903a92e2ddc9>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/ced0da8b8b99be7469c19cb78501ae0cbb31cf7a>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/e77d56766fae84a748bbf2cd1bd822a386a089c8>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/41e4739f163346b3924e25700c4e974123e75cb5>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/cfc991274bc3e9c0b84386fffab754609e3b05df>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/ef112818dec00fdbd1574efdb1bed937247c1f57>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/413a4870b2d8606e62961bf87d3c77cfc7b3048b>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/85d75439d4c0cb4de3e85da06f04d84efb8d08e6>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/93dd751686c65380f05cb17ba8fdbd3c3e189be9>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/2bb93e92582f11fa6d1616ab52d95b49e553cd26>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/292e2d40a882ad6b86315c4ff1f8c89124e50261>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/person/ucl/850795963db4be6481fcc414fe1c3ee61d05b9d8>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Jacaric acid incorporation, breast cancer, ferroptosis"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> "Medicine, Health and Life Sciences";
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/HEAL>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TECH>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.14428/DVN/HF01QB>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/bibliographicCitation> "Cuvelier, Géraldine; Vermonden Perrine; Debisschop Pauline; Martin Manon; Derouane Françoise; Liebisch Gerhard; Ecker Josef; Berlière Martine; Van Bockstal Mieke R; Galant Christine; Duhoux François P.; Hutten Stefan J.; Jonkers Jos; Mourao Larissa; Scheele Colinda L. G. J.; Feron Olivier; Rezsohazy René; Corbet Cyril; Larondelle Yvan, 2024, \"Replication Data for: \"Jacaric acid empowers RSL3-induced ferroptotic cell death in both 2D and 3D breast cancer models\"\", https://doi.org/10.14428/DVN/HF01QB, Open Data @ UCLouvain, V1";
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b54395_b54394_b54393_df_12_69253;
