    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#mobilityTheme> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/public-transport-scheduled-transport>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/timetables-static>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/stop-facilities-location-and-features>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/hours-of-operation>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/operational-calendar>;
