    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#mobilityTheme> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/static-road-network-data>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/static-traffic-signs-and-regulations>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/parking-service-and-rest-area-information>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/dynamic-traffic-signs-and-regulations>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/general-information-for-trip-planning>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/road-work-information>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/road-events-and-conditions>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/road-weather-conditions>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/real-time-traffic-data>;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#transportMode> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/motorcycle>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/truck>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/car>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/8a2102a4-79cf-448c-a200-6cba371dfd72/resource/40238533-5323-412d-91d3-2195ee1237e7>.
