<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#fd676a7bcb1a8742322cab872a4c5246>.
<#fd676a7bcb1a8742322cab872a4c5246> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/6097c3a0-79ab-4e2d-b4cc-0587e46dddf6>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:32:56.562Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#fd676a7bcb1a8742322cab872a4c5246> {
<https://transportdata.be/dataset/6097c3a0-79ab-4e2d-b4cc-0587e46dddf6> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/NLD>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "6097c3a0-79ab-4e2d-b4cc-0587e46dddf6";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Verkeersborden.Vlaanderen - Opstellingen"@nl, "Panneaux de signalisation.Flandre - Constellations"@fr-t-nl, "Verkehrszeichen.Flandern - Sternbilder"@de-t-nl, "Traffic signs.Flanders - Constellations"@en-t-nl;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Puntenlaag van alle opstellingen en bijhorende aanzichten zoals opgenomen in de Verkeersborden.Vlaanderen toepassing. Deze worden voorgesteld al een punt per opstelling/aanzicht en dus zullen er meerdere punten op elkaar liggen indien de opstelling bestaat uit meerdere aanzichten. Er is een link tussen de deze dataset en de borden  (https://www.transportdata.be/nl/dataset/verkeersborden-vlaanderen-borden) zodat je kan weten welke borden aan welke opstelling/aanzicht hangen."@nl, "Couche de points de toutes les configurations et vues associées incluses dans l'application Traffic Signs.Flanders. Ceux-ci sont déjà proposés un point par configuration / vue et il y aura donc plusieurs points les uns sur les autres si la configuration se compose de plusieurs vues. Il existe un lien entre cet ensemble de données et les signes (https://www.transportdata.be/nl/dataset/traffic signs-vlaanderen-signs) afin que vous puissiez savoir quels signes s’accrochent à quelle configuration/vue."@fr-t-nl, "Punktebene aller Setups und zugehörigen Ansichten, wie sie in der Anwendung Traffic Signs.Flanders enthalten sind. Diese werden bereits einen Punkt pro Einrichtung/Ansicht vorgeschlagen, so dass mehrere Punkte übereinander liegen, wenn die Einrichtung aus mehreren Ansichten besteht. Es besteht eine Verbindung zwischen diesem Datensatz und den Schildern (https://www.transportdata.be/nl/dataset/traffic signs-vlaanderen-signs), damit Sie wissen, welche Schilder an welcher Einrichtung/Ansicht hängen."@de-t-nl, "Point layer of all setups and associated views as included in the Traffic Signs.Flanders application. These are already proposed one point per set-up/view and so there will be several points on top of each other if the set-up consists of several views. There is a link between this dataset and the signs (https://www.transportdata.be/nl/dataset/traffic signs-vlaanderen-signs) so that you can know which signs hang on which setup/view."@en-t-nl;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2024-08-02T06:40:35.718425"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-12-18T12:05:55.835664"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeEstablishmentUnit/2143729494>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/applicableLegislation> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg_del/2017/1926/oj>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TRAN>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/6097c3a0-79ab-4e2d-b4cc-0587e46dddf6#>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b54716_b54715_b54714_df_12_69480;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <https://sws.geonames.org/3337388/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/IRREG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b54716_b54715_b54714_df_12_69481;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dqv#qualityAnnotation> _:b54716_b54715_b54714_df_12_69482;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#georeferencingMethod> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/georeferencing-method/other>;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#mobilityTheme> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/static-traffic-signs-and-regulations>;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#transportMode> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/car>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/truck>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/bicycle>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/motorcycle>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/pedestrian>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/6097c3a0-79ab-4e2d-b4cc-0587e46dddf6/resource/195be657-8bfd-41ab-ada6-0004ee3ed563>.
_:b54716_b54715_b54714_df_12_69480 a <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Kind>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#fn> "Agentschap Wegen en Verkeer";
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasEmail> <mailto:wegen.verkeer@mow.vlaanderen.be>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasTelephone> <tel:+3225537901>.
_:b54716_b54715_b54714_df_12_69481 a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2024-08-02T08:30:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
_:b54716_b54715_b54714_df_12_69482 a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dqv#QualityAnnotation>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/oa#hasBody> "http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/63236b7128d642e2a86d55d8b03caaf52-A789CDF63874D84B7D7208C347D31F14"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI>
}
<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#bdcf5557be93a3ad3ac2471894fe3518>.
<#bdcf5557be93a3ad3ac2471894fe3518> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/083cb5d5-bff6-475a-98cb-cfce932647ef>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:32:56.567Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#bdcf5557be93a3ad3ac2471894fe3518> {
<https://transportdata.be/dataset/083cb5d5-bff6-475a-98cb-cfce932647ef> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/NLD>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "083cb5d5-bff6-475a-98cb-cfce932647ef";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Verkeersborden.Vlaanderen - Borden"@nl, "Panneaux de signalisation.Flandre - Panneaux de signalisation"@fr-t-nl, "Verkehrszeichen.Flandern - Schilder"@de-t-nl, "Traffic signs.Flanders - Signs"@en-t-nl;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Puntenlaag van alle verkeersborden zoals opgenomen in de Verkeersborden.Vlaanderen toepassing. \r\nDeze worden voorgesteld al een punt per bord en dus zullen er meerdere punten op elkaar liggen indien de opstelling bestaat uit meerdere borden. \r\nAls attribuut kan je buiten de bordcode en het mogelijke opschrift ook de grootte van het bord, opstelhoogte, ... terugvinden.\r\nEen overicht van de meest gebruikte bordcodes vind je via volgende link: https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1707836168/overzicht_verkeersborden_i27arj.pdf"@nl, "Couche de tous les panneaux de signalisation tels qu'ils figurent dans l'application Traffic Signs.Flanders. \nCeux-ci sont déjà suggérés un point par tableau et il y aura donc plusieurs points les uns sur les autres si la configuration se compose de plusieurs tableaux. \nEn tant qu'attribut, outre le code du tableau et l'inscription possible, vous pouvez également trouver la taille du tableau, la hauteur de réglage, .... \nUn aperçu des codes de tableau les plus couramment utilisés peut être trouvé via le lien suivant: https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1707836168/overview_traffic signs_i27arj.pdf"@fr-t-nl, "Punktebene aller Verkehrszeichen, wie sie in der Anwendung Traffic Signs.Flanders enthalten sind. \nDiese werden bereits ein Punkt pro Board vorgeschlagen und so gibt es mehrere Punkte übereinander, wenn das Setup aus mehreren Boards besteht. \nAls Attribut finden Sie neben dem Boardcode und der möglichen Beschriftung auch die Größe des Boards, die Aufbauhöhe, .... \nEine Übersicht der am häufigsten verwendeten Boardcodes finden Sie unter folgendem Link: https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1707836168/übersicht_Verkehrszeichen_i27arj.pdf"@de-t-nl, "Point layer of all traffic signs as included in the Traffic Signs.Flanders application. \nThese are already suggested one point per board and so there will be several points on top of each other if the setup consists of several boards. \nAs an attribute, besides the board code and the possible inscription, you can also find the size of the board, set-up height, .... \nAn overview of the most commonly used board codes can be found via the following link: https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1707836168/overview_traffic signs_i27arj.pdf"@en-t-nl;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2024-06-27T12:29:25.365183"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-12-18T12:05:54.553667"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeEstablishmentUnit/2143729494>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/applicableLegislation> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg_del/2017/1926/oj>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TRAN>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/083cb5d5-bff6-475a-98cb-cfce932647ef#>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b54719_b54718_b54717_df_12_69483;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <https://sws.geonames.org/3337388/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/IRREG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b54719_b54718_b54717_df_12_69484;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dqv#qualityAnnotation> _:b54719_b54718_b54717_df_12_69485;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#georeferencingMethod> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/georeferencing-method/other>;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#mobilityTheme> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/static-traffic-signs-and-regulations>;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#transportMode> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/car>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/truck>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/motorcycle>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/bicycle>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/pedestrian>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/083cb5d5-bff6-475a-98cb-cfce932647ef/resource/230f490b-1a3e-491b-8ed9-faf2c8aa357b>.
_:b54719_b54718_b54717_df_12_69483 a <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Kind>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#fn> "Agentschap Wegen en Verkeer";
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasEmail> <mailto:wegen.verkeer@mow.vlaanderen.be>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasTelephone> <tel:+3225537901>.
