<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#01806932c22989a5fd55f82a9f1d0e05>.
<#01806932c22989a5fd55f82a9f1d0e05> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/ef98f1a2-4a77-4327-bc5a-99a3c66bed80>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:32:56.662Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#01806932c22989a5fd55f82a9f1d0e05> {
<https://transportdata.be/dataset/ef98f1a2-4a77-4327-bc5a-99a3c66bed80> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "ef98f1a2-4a77-4327-bc5a-99a3c66bed80";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "SNCB GFTS - scheduled timetable and real-time data"@en, "NMBS GFTS - geplande dienstregeling en real-time gegevens"@nl-t-en, "SNCB GFTS - horaires programmés et données en temps réel"@fr-t-en, "SNCB GFTS - Fahrplan und Echtzeitdaten"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Que ce soient les données de planification ou en temps réel, nous les mettons à votre disposition. Et ceci, gratuitement !\r\n\r\nConcrètement, deux flux GTFS sont proposés :\r\nLes données de planification, mises à jour tous les jours\r\nLes données en temps réel, mises à jour toutes les 30 secondes\r\n"@fr, "Ob es sich dabei um die Planungsdaten oder die Echtzeitdaten handelt, wir stellen sie Ihnen zur Verfügung. Und das kostenlos! Konkret bieten wir zwei GTFS-Feeds an:\r\nDie Planungsdaten, die täglich aktualisiert werden\r\nDie Echtzeitdaten, die alle 30 Sekunden aktualisiert werden."@de, "Of je nu de geplande dienstregeling of de realtime gegevens nodig hebt, we stellen ze allebei gratis tot je beschikking! Er zijn twee GTFS-feeds beschikbaar:\r\nDe geplande gegevens die elke dag geüpdatet worden\r\nDe realtime gegevens die om de 30 seconden geüpdatet worden."@nl, "Both the scheduled timetable and the real-time data are available to you for free. There are two GTFS feeds available:\r\n\r\n - The scheduled data which are updated daily\r\n - The real-time data which are updated every 30 seconds"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-02-06T10:45:00.245091"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-12-18T12:05:25.335767"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeRegisteredEntity/0203430576>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/applicableLegislation> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg_del/2017/1926/oj>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TRAN>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/ef98f1a2-4a77-4327-bc5a-99a3c66bed80#>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b54782_b54781_b54780_df_12_69526;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <https://sws.geonames.org/2802361/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/1MIN>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b54782_b54781_b54780_df_12_69527;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#mobilityTheme> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/public-transport-scheduled-transport>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/real-time-estimated-departure-and-arrival-times>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/timetables-static>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/transport-operators>;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#transportMode> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/regional-and-local-rail>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/ef98f1a2-4a77-4327-bc5a-99a3c66bed80/resource/1d19dde0-e56e-41d7-891d-c9fae3c21cdc>.
_:b54782_b54781_b54780_df_12_69526 a <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Kind>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#fn> "Arnaud Wattiez";
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasEmail> <mailto:gtfs@sncb.be>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasTelephone> <tel:+32000000000>.
_:b54782_b54781_b54780_df_12_69527 a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2020-02-06T11:40:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>
}
<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#ca341bf497c4cd38fef24208e932a94e>.
<#ca341bf497c4cd38fef24208e932a94e> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/f437463b-fe0a-4960-8736-599442d698b7>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:32:56.666Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#ca341bf497c4cd38fef24208e932a94e> {
<https://transportdata.be/dataset/f437463b-fe0a-4960-8736-599442d698b7> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "f437463b-fe0a-4960-8736-599442d698b7";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "SNCB - Carbon footprint of travel per passenger kilometer"@en, "NMBS - Koolstofvoetafdruk van reizen per passagierskilometer"@nl-t-en, "SNCB - Empreinte carbone des déplacements par passager-kilomètre"@fr-t-en, "SNCB - CO2-Fußabdruck des Verkehrs pro Passagierkilometer"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "SNCB - Empreinte carbone des déplacements par passager kilomètre. Données précises pour la SNCB non disponibles. Cependant, le ministère britannique des affaires, de l'énergie et de la stratégie industrielle (BEIS) a estimé en 2018 que les émissions de gaz à effet de serre par passager-kilomètre pour National Rail étaient de 41 g. (Les données sont basées sur les facteurs de conversion officiels utilisés dans les rapports du Royaume-Uni. Ces facteurs peuvent varier légèrement en fonction du pays et de l'occupation supposée des trains.)"@fr, "SNCB - CO2-Fußabdruck des Reisens pro Personenkilometer. Genaue Daten für SNCB nicht verfügbar. Das britische Department for Business, Energy & Industrial Strategy (BEIS) schätzte jedoch im Jahr 2018, dass die Treibhausgasemissionen pro Personenkilometer für National Rail 41 g betragen. (Die Daten basieren auf offiziellen Umrechnungsfaktoren, die in der britischen Berichterstattung verwendet werden. Diese Faktoren können je nach Land und angenommener Auslastung der Züge leicht variieren.)"@de, "NMBS - Carbon footprint van reizen per reizigerskilometer. Precieze gegevens voor NMBS niet beschikbaar. Het UK Department for Business, Energy & Industrial Strategy (BEIS) schatte in 2018 echter dat de uitstoot van broeikasgassen per passagierskilometer voor National Rail 41 g bedroeg. (De gegevens zijn gebaseerd op officiële conversiefactoren die worden gebruikt in de Britse rapportage. Deze factoren kunnen enigszins variëren, afhankelijk van het land en de veronderstelde bezetting van treinen.)"@nl, "SNCB - Carbon footprint of travel per passenger kilometer. Precise data for SNCB not available. However, UK Department for Business, Energy & Industrial Strategy (BEIS) estimated in 2018 that the Greenhouse gas emissions per passenger kilometer for National Rail was 41g. (Data is based on official conversion factors used in UK reporting. These factors may vary slightly depending on the country, and assumed occupancy of trains.)"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2022-07-28T07:53:03.421399"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-12-18T12:05:24.716349"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeRegisteredEntity/0203430576>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/applicableLegislation> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg_del/2017/1926/oj>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TRAN>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/f437463b-fe0a-4960-8736-599442d698b7#>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b54785_b54784_b54783_df_12_69528;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <https://sws.geonames.org/2802361/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/IRREG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b54785_b54784_b54783_df_12_69529;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#mobilityTheme> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/public-transport-scheduled-transport>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/environmental-standards-for-vehicles>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/transport-operators>;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#transportMode> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/regional-and-local-rail>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/f437463b-fe0a-4960-8736-599442d698b7/resource/b798a7ef-3fff-431f-9e30-f678ad449f87>.
_:b54785_b54784_b54783_df_12_69528 a <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Kind>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#fn> "Arnaud WATTIEZ";
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasEmail> <mailto:arnaud.wattiez@b-rail.be>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasTelephone> <tel:+32475293916>.
_:b54785_b54784_b54783_df_12_69529 a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2022-07-28T09:47:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>
}
