<#4ac0851932376d4ce5c693eb46876c99> {
<https://transportdata.be/dataset/4d7de66c-8847-4940-807b-c1c85aa78dad> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "4d7de66c-8847-4940-807b-c1c85aa78dad";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "SNCB Basic common standard fares"@en, "NMBS Gemeenschappelijke basistarieven"@nl-t-en, "SNCB Tarifs standard communs de base"@fr-t-en, "SNCB Allgemeine Standardtarife"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "URL : Transport Ticket Prices : https://www.belgiantrain.be/en/support/terms-and-conditions-for-transport \r\nURL for Exchange/Refunds/Replacement/Transfer : https://www.belgiantrain.be/en/support/faq/faq-tickets-and-railcards/faq-exchange-refund\r\nUpdated at least 1x per year in February\r\n\r\nIndien u NMBS-tickets wenst door te verkopen als Mobility Service Provider en toegang heeft tot de resale API, ga dan naar https://www.belgiantrain.be/nl/3rd-party-services/mobility-service-providers/msp"@nl, "URL : Transport Ticket Prices : https://www.belgiantrain.be/en/support/terms-and-conditions-for-transport \r\nURL for Exchange/Refunds/Replacement/Transfer : https://www.belgiantrain.be/en/support/faq/faq-tickets-and-railcards/faq-exchange-refund\r\nUpdated at least 1x per year in February\r\n\r\nSi vous souhaitez revendre des tickets SNCB en tant que Mobility Service Provider et avoir accès à l'API de revente, rendez-vous sur https://www.belgiantrain.be/fr/3rd-party-services/mobility-service-providers/msp"@fr, "URL : Transport Ticket Prices : https://www.belgiantrain.be/en/support/terms-and-conditions-for-transport \r\nURL for Exchange/Refunds/Replacement/Transfer : https://www.belgiantrain.be/en/support/faq/faq-tickets-and-railcards/faq-exchange-refund\r\nUpdated at least 1x per year in February\r\n\r\nIf you want to resell SNCB tickets as a Mobility Service Provider and have access to the resale API, go to https://www.belgiantrain.be/en/3rd-party-services/mobility-service-providers/msp"@de, "URL : Transport Ticket Prices : https://www.belgiantrain.be/en/support/terms-and-conditions-for-transport \r\nURL for Exchange/Refunds/Replacement/Transfer : https://www.belgiantrain.be/en/support/faq/faq-tickets-and-railcards/faq-exchange-refund\r\nUpdated at least 1x per year in February\r\n\r\nIf you want to resell SNCB tickets as a Mobility Service Provider and have access to the resale API, go to https://www.belgiantrain.be/en/3rd-party-services/mobility-service-providers/msp\r\n"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-09-10T07:38:38.665297"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-12-18T12:05:23.456467"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
