<#20d23217173cf1260a402ec8508f70d4> {
<https://transportdata.be/dataset/e6b735f2-2e23-4d4d-be59-124d95ca63ba> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "e6b735f2-2e23-4d4d-be59-124d95ca63ba";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "real time CoopStroom electrical vehicles"@en, "real time CoopStroom elektrische voertuigen"@nl-t-en, "Véhicules électriques CoopStroom en temps réel"@fr-t-en, "CoopStroom Elektrofahrzeuge in Echtzeit"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This rich JSON feed contains the realtime status and position (updated every 5 minutes) de realtime of the shared cars of CoopStroom. The feed contains: geoPosition: longitude - longitude of the geolocation. geoPosition: latitude - latitude of the geolocation. displayName - Name of the car sharing station vehicleInformation: brand - brand of the car vehicleInformation: model - model of the car vehicleInformation: fuelType - type of fuel vehicleInformation: transmissionType - type of transmission stationType - type of usage (fixed station / free floating )"@en, "Deze rijke JSON feed bevat de realtime status en positie (elke 5 minuten bijgewerkt) van de deelauto's van CoopStroom. Het voer bevat: geoPositie: lengtegraad - lengtegraad van de geolocatie. geoPositie: breedtegraad - breedtegraad van de geolocatie. displayNaam - Naam van het voertuig van het deelstationInformatie: merk - merk van het voertuigInformatie: model - model van het voertuigInformatie: fuelType - type brandstofvoertuigInformatie: transmissieType - type transmissiestationType - type gebruik (vast station / vrij zwevend )"@nl-t-en, "Ce riche flux JSON contient l'état et la position en temps réel (mis à jour toutes les 5 minutes) des voitures partagées de CoopStroom. L'aliment contient: géoPosition: longitude - longitude de la géolocalisation. geoPosition: latitude - latitude de la géolocalisation. displayName - Nom du véhicule de la station d'autopartageInformation: marque - marque du véhicule automobileInformation: modèle - modèle du véhicule automobileInformation: fuelType - type de véhicule à carburantInformations: transmissionType - type de station de transmissionType - type d'utilisation (station fixe / flottante libre )"@fr-t-en, "Dieser umfangreiche JSON-Feed enthält den Echtzeitstatus und die Position (alle 5 Minuten aktualisiert) der gemeinsam genutzten Autos von CoopStroom. Das Futter enthält: geoPosition: Länge - Länge der Geolokalisierung. geoPosition: Breitengrad - Breitengrad der Geolokalisierung. displayName - Name des Carsharing-StationsfahrzeugsInformationen: Marke - Marke des FahrzeugsInformationen: Modell - Modell des FahrzeugsInformationen: fuelType - Typ des KraftstofffahrzeugsInformationen: transmissionType - Typ der ÜbertragungsstationType - Art der Nutzung (feste Station / frei schwimmend )"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2023-09-27T13:17:46.916253"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-12-18T12:04:40.603512"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeRegisteredEntity/0675918368>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/applicableLegislation> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg_del/2017/1926/oj>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TRAN>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/e6b735f2-2e23-4d4d-be59-124d95ca63ba#>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b54851_b54850_b54849_df_12_69579;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <https://sws.geonames.org/3337388/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/IRREG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b54851_b54850_b54849_df_12_69580;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#georeferencingMethod> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/georeferencing-method/other>;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#mobilityTheme> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/sharing-and-hiring-services>;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#transportMode> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/car-sharing>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/e6b735f2-2e23-4d4d-be59-124d95ca63ba/resource/914af5b3-6220-4fc4-b12f-06be5792f954>.
_:b54851_b54850_b54849_df_12_69579 a <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Kind>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#fn> "Cedric Depuydt";
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasEmail> <mailto:autodelen@coopstroom.be>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasTelephone> <tel:+32476777766>.
_:b54851_b54850_b54849_df_12_69580 a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>;
