<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#462f05278c39880faeb70115adb8a633>.
<#462f05278c39880faeb70115adb8a633> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/36b68214-a538-40f3-a62b-e82205769fe2>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:32:56.905Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#462f05278c39880faeb70115adb8a633> {
<https://transportdata.be/dataset/36b68214-a538-40f3-a62b-e82205769fe2> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/FRA>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/NLD>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "36b68214-a538-40f3-a62b-e82205769fe2";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Brussels Regional Cycle Routes"@en, "Brusselse regionale fietsroutes"@nl-t-en, "Itinéraires cyclables régionaux de Bruxelles"@fr-t-en, "Regionale Fahrradrouten in Brüssel"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Les [itinéraires cyclables régionaux](http://data-mobility.brussels/mobigis?x=485352.9798586729&y=6593040.226464508&zoom=12&baselayer=mapquest&layers=icr%3B&opacity=1%3B&filter=) sont des cheminements recommandés pour des déplacements à vélo de moyenne et longue distance à travers plusieurs communes. En règle générale, ces itinéraires empruntent des voiries locales, où le trafic est moins dense, moins rapide, et donc moins stressant que sur les voiries principales. Mais le franchissement de certains obstacles naturels ou artificiels (pont franchissant une vallée, le canal, une autoroute, passage sous une ligne de chemin de fer, etc.) ramène parfois les itinéraires sur les grands axes.\r\n"@fr, "De [gewestelijke fietsroutes](http://data-mobility.brussels/mobigis?x=485352.9798586729&y=6593040.226464508&zoom=12&baselayer=mapquest&layers=icr%3B&opacity=1%3B&filter=) zijn aanbevolen fietswegen voor verplaatsingen op middellange en lange afstand die door verschillende gemeenten lopen. In het algemeen volgen deze routes lokale wegen, omdat het verkeer er minder druk is, minder snel verloopt en dus minder stresserend is dan op de hoofdwegen. Vermits bepaalde natuurlijke of kunstmatige obstakels (brug over een dal, een kanaal, een autosnelweg, doorgang onder een spoorweg, enz.) moeten worden genomen, lopen de routes echter soms ook over grotere verkeersaders.\r\n"@nl, "[Regional cycle routes](http://data-mobility.brussels/mobigis?x=485352.9798586729&y=6593040.226464508&zoom=12&baselayer=mapquest&layers=icr%3B&opacity=1%3B&filter=) are recommended routes for medium and long distance bicycle journeys through several municipalities. As a general rule, these routes use local roads, where traffic is less dense, slower, and therefore less stressful than on the main roads. But crossing certain natural or artificial obstacles (bridge crossing a valley, the canal, a motorway, crossing under a railway line, etc.) sometimes brings back the routes on the main axes.\r\n"@en, "[Regionale Radrouten](http://data-mobility.brussels/mobigis?x=485352.9798586729&y=6593040.226464508&zoom=12&baselayer=mapquest&layers=icr%3B&opacity=1%3B&filter=) sind empfohlene Routen für Mittel- und Fernradreisen durch mehrere Gemeinden. In der Regel nutzen diese Routen lokale Straßen, auf denen der Verkehr weniger dicht, langsamer und daher weniger stressig ist als auf den Hauptstraßen. Aber das Überqueren bestimmter natürlicher oder künstlicher Hindernisse (Brücke, die ein Tal, den Kanal, eine Autobahn, das Überqueren einer Eisenbahnlinie usw. überquert) bringt manchmal die Routen auf den Hauptachsen zurück."@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-02-11T10:18:58.215301"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-12-18T12:04:04.908685"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeRegisteredEntity/0316381039>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/applicableLegislation> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg_del/2017/1926/oj>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TRAN>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/36b68214-a538-40f3-a62b-e82205769fe2#>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b54929_b54928_b54927_df_12_69634;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <https://sws.geonames.org/2800867/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/IRREG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b54929_b54928_b54927_df_12_69635;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#mobilityTheme> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/cycle-network-data>;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#transportMode> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/transport-mode/bicycle>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/36b68214-a538-40f3-a62b-e82205769fe2/resource/7b790d28-d167-4c8c-84f8-3dfd4d32226c>.
_:b54929_b54928_b54927_df_12_69634 a <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Kind>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#fn> "Brussels Mobility";
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasEmail> <mailto:mobilite@sprb.brussels>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#hasTelephone> <tel:+3280094001>.
_:b54929_b54928_b54927_df_12_69635 a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2020-01-01T00:00:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>
}
<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#32590cb67b63160aa0f3892b5a276a22>.
<#32590cb67b63160aa0f3892b5a276a22> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/77dd083b-440b-44a8-8db8-c4c4654fc46b>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:32:56.910Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#32590cb67b63160aa0f3892b5a276a22> {
<https://transportdata.be/dataset/77dd083b-440b-44a8-8db8-c4c4654fc46b> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/FRA>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/NLD>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "77dd083b-440b-44a8-8db8-c4c4654fc46b";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Brussels Pedestrian Network"@en, "Pedestrian Network Brussel"@nl-t-en, "Réseau piétonnier de Bruxelles"@fr-t-en, "Brüsseler Fußgängernetz"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Voetgangersnetwerk van het Brussels Hoofdstedelijk Gewest.   \r\nDit netwerk bestaat enerzijds uit het [structurerend netwerk](https://data.mobility.brussels/fr/info/pedestrian_network/) dat is gedefinieerd in de multimodale specialisatie van wegen, en anderzijds uit [trage wegen](https://data.mobility.brussels/fr/info/stapas/)."@nl, "Réseau piétons de la Région de Bruxelles Capitale.   \r\nCe réseau est composé d'une part du [réseau structurant](https://data.mobility.brussels/fr/info/pedestrian_network/) défini dans la spécialisation multimodale des voiries, et d'autre part des [voies lentes](https://data.mobility.brussels/fr/info/stapas/)."@fr, "Pedestrian network of the Brussels Capital Region.   \r\nThis network is made up on the one hand of the [structuring network](https://data.mobility.brussels/fr/info/pedestrian_network/) defined in the multimodal specialization of roads, and on the other hand of [slow ways](https://data.mobility.brussels/fr/info/stapas/)."@en, "Fußgängernetz der Region Brüssel-Hauptstadt.  \nDieses Netz besteht zum einen aus dem [Strukturierungsnetz] (https://data.mobility.brussels/fr/info/pedestrian_network/), das in der multimodalen Spezialisierung von Straßen definiert ist, und zum anderen aus [slow ways] (https://data.mobility.brussels/fr/info/stapas/)."@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2020-06-02T10:03:33.823484"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-12-18T12:04:03.650542"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeRegisteredEntity/0316381039>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/applicableLegislation> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg_del/2017/1926/oj>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TRAN>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/77dd083b-440b-44a8-8db8-c4c4654fc46b#>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b54932_b54931_b54930_df_12_69636;
