    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b54935_b54934_b54933_df_12_69639;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#mobilityTheme> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/filling-and-charging-stations>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/static-traffic-signs-and-regulations>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/static-road-network-data>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/road-work-information>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/general-information-for-trip-planning>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/road-events-and-conditions>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/road-weather-conditions>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/public-transport-non-scheduled-transport>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/public-transport-scheduled-transport>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/sharing-and-hiring-services>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/parking-service-and-rest-area-information>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/pedestrian-network-data>, <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-theme/cycle-network-data>;
