    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "97523844-af25-4d08-890f-e30b59839343";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Brussels Collecto stops"@en, "Brussel Collecto stopt"@nl-t-en, "Le Collecto de Bruxelles s'arrête"@fr-t-en, "Brüssel Collecto stoppt"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "De locaties van de [Collecto](https://mobilite-mobiliteit.brussels/nl/collecto) stopplaatsen in het Brussels Hoofdstedelijk Gewest. Collecto is een collectieve taxidienst die zeven dagen op zeven beschikbaar is tussen 23 uur 's avonds en 6 uur 's ochtends, en dit in het hele Brussels Hoofdstedelijk Gewest. Collecto bedient momenteel meer dan 200 [vertrekpunten](https://data-mobility.brussels/mobigis/nl/?x=485352.9798586729&y=6593040.226464508&zoom=12&baselayer=urbis&layers=Collecto_stops%3B&opacity=1%3B&filter=) (gelegen aan de MIVB-haltes)."@nl, "[Collecto](https://mobilite-mobiliteit.brussels/fr/collecto) est un service de taxis collectifs disponible 7 jours sur 7 entre 23 heures et 6 heures du matin sur tout le [territoire](https://data-mobility.brussels/mobigis/fr/?x=485352.9798586729&y=6593040.226464508&zoom=12&baselayer=urbis&layers=Collecto_stops%3B&opacity=1%3B&filter=) de la Région de Bruxelles-Capitale."@fr, "[Collecto](https://mobilite-mobiliteit.brussels/en/collecto) is a collective taxi service available every day between 11 PM and 6 AM [everywhere](https://data-mobility.brussels/mobigis/en/?x=485352.9798586729&y=6593040.226464508&zoom=12&baselayer=urbis&layers=Collecto_stops%3B&opacity=1%3B&filter=) in the Brussels-Capital Region."@en, "[Collecto](https://mobilite-mobiliteit.brussels/de/collecto) ist ein Sammeltaxidienst, der täglich zwischen 23:00 und 06:00 Uhr [überall](https://data-mobility.brussels/mobigis/de/?x=485352.9798586729&y=6593040.226464508&zoom=12&baselayer=urbis&layers=Collecto_stops%3B&opacity=1%3B&filter=) in der Region Brüssel-Hauptstadt zur Verfügung steht."@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2019-12-24T09:12:18.101531"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2024-12-18T12:04:00.736773"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeRegisteredEntity/0316381039>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/applicableLegislation> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg_del/2017/1926/oj>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TRAN>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://transportdata.be/dataset/97523844-af25-4d08-890f-e30b59839343#>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> _:b54938_b54937_b54936_df_12_69640;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <https://sws.geonames.org/2800867/>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accrualPeriodicity> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/frequency/IRREG>;
