    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:32:56.943Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#d63c4fa91f5e0941b63e788727fc75a6> {
<https://transportdata.be/dataset/e9e63348-c1c4-460d-af61-e96febb9eacc> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "e9e63348-c1c4-460d-af61-e96febb9eacc";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Belgian Transport Emissions from 1990"@en, "Belgische vervoersemissies vanaf 1990"@nl-t-en, "Émissions belges des transports à partir de 1990"@fr-t-en, "Belgische Verkehrsemissionen ab 1990"@de-t-en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Dataset met contextuele gegevens over Belgische transportemissies vanaf 1990:\r\n- Geografische begrenzing: nationaal (België)\r\n- Jaar/jaren: 1990 tot jaar X-2 (jaarlijkse update van alle jaren vanaf 1990)\r\n- Categorieën: vervoerswijzen (binnenlandse luchtvaart, internationale luchtvaart, wegvervoer [auto's, lichte vrachtwagens, zware vrachtwagens, motorfietsen, overige], spoorwegen, binnenlandse scheepvaart, internationale scheepvaart, overig vervoer, vervoer via pijpleidingen, overige].\r\n- Variabelen en eenheden: emissie van broeikasgassen (geaggregeerd of CO2, CH4, N2O, CO, NOx, SO2, NMVOC) in kt of ktCO2eq, brandstofverbruik in TJ, impliciete emissiefactoren (gewicht van uitgestoten broeikasgassen per energie-inhoud van brandstof) per type gas en per type brandstof in t/TJ of kg/TJ.\r\nLinks:\r\n* Belgian EU GHG inventory submission – from 2024 onwards (January and March of each year): https://cdr.eionet.europa.eu/be/eu/govreg/inventory/ \r\n* Belgian EU GHG inventory submission – until 2023 (yearly, from 2015 onwards, January and March of each year): https://cdr.eionet.europa.eu/ReportekEngine/searchdataflow?dataflow_uris=http%3A%2F%2Frod.eionet.europa.eu%2Fobligations%2F701&years%3Aint%3Aignore_empty=&partofyear=&reportingdate_start%3Adate%3Aignore_empty=&reportingdate_end%3Adate%3Aignore_empty=&country=http%3A%2F%2Frod.eionet.europa.eu%2Fspatial%2F5&release_status=anystatus&sort_on=reportingdate&sort_order=reverse&batch_size\r\n* Belgian UNFCCC GHG inventory submission (yearly, from 2003, May of each year): https://unfccc.int/ghg-inventories-annex-i-parties/2023\r\n* EU EEA greenhouse gas data viewer: https://www.eea.europa.eu/data-and-maps/data/data-viewers/greenhouse-gases-viewer \r\n* UNFCCC Greenhouse Gas Inventory Data portal (https://di.unfccc.int/): flexible query (https://di.unfccc.int/flex_annex1).\r\n* National climate Commission (yearly, from 2014, January, March and May of each year): Reports | National Climate Commission (cnc-nkc.be) https://www.cnc-nkc.be/en/reports  > GHG inventory \r\n\r\n(see most recent dataset submission for more details, only in english)"@nl, "Ensemble de données contextuelles sur les émissions des transports belges depuis 1990 :\r\n- Limite géographique : nationale (Belgique)\r\n- Année(s) : de 1990 à l'année X-2 (mise à jour annuelle de toutes les années à partir de 1990)\r\n- Catégories : modes de transport (aviation intérieure, aviation internationale, transport routier [voitures, véhicules utilitaires légers, véhicules utilitaires lourds, motocycles, autres], chemins de fer, navigation intérieure, navigation internationale, autres transports, transport par conduites, autres].\r\n- Variables et unités : émissions de gaz à effet de serre (agrégées ou CO2, CH4, N2O, CO, NOx, SO2, NMVOC) en kt ou ktCO2eq, consommation de carburant en TJ, facteurs d'émission implicites (poids des gaz à effet de serre émis par contenu énergétique du carburant) par type de gaz et par type de carburant en t/TJ ou kg/TJ.\r\n\r\nLinks:\r\n* Belgian EU GHG inventory submission – from 2024 onwards (January and March of each year): https://cdr.eionet.europa.eu/be/eu/govreg/inventory/ \r\n* Belgian EU GHG inventory submission – until 2023 (yearly, from 2015 onwards, January and March of each year): https://cdr.eionet.europa.eu/ReportekEngine/searchdataflow?dataflow_uris=http%3A%2F%2Frod.eionet.europa.eu%2Fobligations%2F701&years%3Aint%3Aignore_empty=&partofyear=&reportingdate_start%3Adate%3Aignore_empty=&reportingdate_end%3Adate%3Aignore_empty=&country=http%3A%2F%2Frod.eionet.europa.eu%2Fspatial%2F5&release_status=anystatus&sort_on=reportingdate&sort_order=reverse&batch_size\r\n* Belgian UNFCCC GHG inventory submission (yearly, from 2003, May of each year): https://unfccc.int/ghg-inventories-annex-i-parties/2023\r\n* EU EEA greenhouse gas data viewer: https://www.eea.europa.eu/data-and-maps/data/data-viewers/greenhouse-gases-viewer \r\n* UNFCCC Greenhouse Gas Inventory Data portal (https://di.unfccc.int/): flexible query (https://di.unfccc.int/flex_annex1).\r\n* National climate Commission (yearly, from 2014, January, March and May of each year): Reports | National Climate Commission (cnc-nkc.be) https://www.cnc-nkc.be/en/reports  > GHG inventory \r\n\r\n(see most recent dataset submission for more details, only in english)"@fr, "Datensatz mit kontextbezogenen Daten über belgische Verkehrsemissionen ab 1990:\r\n- Geografische Begrenzung: national (Belgien)\r\n- Jahr(e): 1990 bis Jahr X-2 (jährliche Aktualisierung aller Jahre ab 1990)\r\n- Kategorien: Verkehrsträger (Inlandsflugverkehr, internationaler Flugverkehr, Straßenverkehr [Pkw, leichte Lkw, schwere Lkw, Motorräder, sonstige], Eisenbahn, Inlandsschifffahrt, internationale Schifffahrt, sonstiger Verkehr, Pipelinetransport, sonstige]\r\n- Variablen und Einheiten: Emission von Treibhausgasen (aggregiert oder CO2, CH4, N2O, CO, NOx, SO2, NMVOC) in kt oder ktCO2eq, Kraftstoffverbrauch in TJ, implizite Emissionsfaktoren (Gewicht der emittierten Treibhausgase pro Energiegehalt des Kraftstoffs) pro Gasart und pro Kraftstoffart in t/TJ oder kg/TJ.\r\nLinks:\r\n* Belgian EU GHG inventory submission – from 2024 onwards (January and March of each year): https://cdr.eionet.europa.eu/be/eu/govreg/inventory/ \r\n* Belgian EU GHG inventory submission – until 2023 (yearly, from 2015 onwards, January and March of each year): https://cdr.eionet.europa.eu/ReportekEngine/searchdataflow?dataflow_uris=http%3A%2F%2Frod.eionet.europa.eu%2Fobligations%2F701&years%3Aint%3Aignore_empty=&partofyear=&reportingdate_start%3Adate%3Aignore_empty=&reportingdate_end%3Adate%3Aignore_empty=&country=http%3A%2F%2Frod.eionet.europa.eu%2Fspatial%2F5&release_status=anystatus&sort_on=reportingdate&sort_order=reverse&batch_size\r\n* Belgian UNFCCC GHG inventory submission (yearly, from 2003, May of each year): https://unfccc.int/ghg-inventories-annex-i-parties/2023\r\n* EU EEA greenhouse gas data viewer: https://www.eea.europa.eu/data-and-maps/data/data-viewers/greenhouse-gases-viewer \r\n* UNFCCC Greenhouse Gas Inventory Data portal (https://di.unfccc.int/): flexible query (https://di.unfccc.int/flex_annex1).\r\n* National climate Commission (yearly, from 2014, January, March and May of each year): Reports | National Climate Commission (cnc-nkc.be) https://www.cnc-nkc.be/en/reports  > GHG inventory \r\n\r\n(see most recent dataset submission for more details, only in english)"@de, "Dataset with contextual data on Belgian transport emissions from 1990:\r\n- Geographical boundary: national (Belgium)\r\n- Year(s): 1990 to year X-2 (yearly update of all years from 1990 onwards)\r\n- Categories: transport modes (domestic aviation, international aviation, road transportation [cars, light duty trucks, heavy duty trucks, motorcycles, other], railways, domestic navigation, international navigation, other transportation, pipeline transport, other]\r\n- Variables and units: emission of GHG gases (aggregated or CO2, CH4, N2O, CO, NOx, SO2, NMVOC) in kt or ktCO2eq, fuel consumption in TJ, implied emission factors (weight of GHG emitted per energy content of fuel) per type of gas and per type of fuel in t/TJ or kg/TJ.\r\n\r\nLinks:\r\n\r\n* Belgian EU GHG inventory submission – from 2024 onwards (January and March of each year): https://cdr.eionet.europa.eu/be/eu/govreg/inventory/ \r\n* Belgian EU GHG inventory submission – until 2023 (yearly, from 2015 onwards, January and March of each year): https://cdr.eionet.europa.eu/ReportekEngine/searchdataflow?dataflow_uris=http%3A%2F%2Frod.eionet.europa.eu%2Fobligations%2F701&years%3Aint%3Aignore_empty=&partofyear=&reportingdate_start%3Adate%3Aignore_empty=&reportingdate_end%3Adate%3Aignore_empty=&country=http%3A%2F%2Frod.eionet.europa.eu%2Fspatial%2F5&release_status=anystatus&sort_on=reportingdate&sort_order=reverse&batch_size\r\n* Belgian UNFCCC GHG inventory submission (yearly, from 2003, May of each year): https://unfccc.int/ghg-inventories-annex-i-parties/2023\r\n* EU EEA greenhouse gas data viewer: https://www.eea.europa.eu/data-and-maps/data/data-viewers/greenhouse-gases-viewer \r\n* UNFCCC Greenhouse Gas Inventory Data portal (https://di.unfccc.int/): flexible query (https://di.unfccc.int/flex_annex1).\r\n* National climate Commission (yearly, from 2014, January, March and May of each year): Reports | National Climate Commission (cnc-nkc.be) https://www.cnc-nkc.be/en/reports  > GHG inventory \r\n\r\n(see most recent dataset submission for more details, only in english)\r\n"@en;
